name: AC pencil
description:
Created in Dreambooth this model provides you the ability to create extremely detailed 2D Illustration pencil Styles.

Making these models can be expensive and very time consuming. If you would consider helping out, it would be much appreciated as any little bit goes a long way

https://www.buymeacoffee.com/Theprotoart

Edit: Better results with detailed prompts but you can also get some really amazing ones with simple ones kind of have to just explore.

If your image has color, try, adding the words, black and white or monochrome or even adding the word, color or colorized in the negative prompt. I have use many prompts from Lexica.art as well as from arthub.ai that have given me some really phenomenal results.

I also show you how to create your own custom models with your own art on my YouTube channel.

Video link

Inspired by Atomic Comics, this a fine-tuned Stable Diffusion model trained on similar work and portrait art. The correct token is evang.

Atomic Comic is not affiliated with this.

Check out my other models: https://civitai.com/user/mrpbody
